" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Koebner reaction in lichen planus",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 396px; height: 260px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Patients with lichen planus can exhibit the Koebner reaction, in which lesions develop in areas of trauma. In this patient, the Koebner reaction resulted from scratching.",
